A pile of rocks with runic marks. Remains of a powerful golem.

properties.text: As you step inside of the room, you feel at utmost certainty that the people responsible of your pitiful state are close.
You see two destroyed golems on the floor and signs of a brief battle. The one who did this must have immense power.
You hear a muffled chanting somewhere from the walls. As your anger rises you spot a single lever in the middle of the room.
